column5: Well hit bass-pro,or better known as my candy store..lol..lol.  . this morning for some new walleye weapons for the bay of quinte,the rapala deep #11 taildancers are new colors for 08-09 called barbie,pink lemonade,old red-eye.  for the reef runners 800 series deep-divers. they are called lights-out,fruit loops,red-hot tiger !!!and of course i got a few new football finnese jigs 1/4oz,3/16oz so i can use with mark kuliks strike-zone baits !!!! so look out walleyes im comming to get you !!!
Real nice assortment you got yourself  Let us know how you do

I was at BPS this morning too Shaun, from 9:30 till 11:00, sorry I missed you.  I just picked up one musky bait I needed for next week, plus I actually did buy a bag of candy from the rack near the checkout counter, so your calling BPS the candy store is pretty accurate

Oh thats too bad lew,i think i got there about 11am !!!im sorry i missed seeing & talking to you, and yes speaking of candy i also bought a big bag of that beef jerky,from the big display by the fish tank...man is that stuff good,expensive but good and it really is just like candy !!!..lol..lol.
umm thats some nice equipment I havent bought lures in 6 months ,good luck out there
heading there tomorrow for some broadheads and camo:D
Gee Shawn... last years colours won't work for you this time! LOL  I'm one to talk... just finished painting over a brand new Legend Perch bait to be the colour I really wanted!
Looks like your ready for them. Always good to get more toys.

Buddy you and I must have the same eye for tackle because I went to BPS on Thursday and bought all the exact same lures.Those new tdd11 by Rapala are awesome looking cranks.The new colours are unreal. Dan
awesome selections for sure ...... best of luck on the BoQ ..... waiting for the reports now
My walleye came in this weekend on a 2 yr old Rapala deep diving tail dancer you guys just want some bling bling lures
